cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.PL, cs.FL, cs.LG

This paper deals with an extension of Metric Temporal Logic ($\mathsf{MTL}$) with counting modalities, which is a topic related to logic and automata theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). However, the paper also discusses the expressive power and decidability of the logic, which are topics related to artificial intelligence and programming languages, respectively. Hence, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.PL (Programming Languages), and cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) are also likely categories. Finally, the paper uses the technique of EF games, which is a topic related to machine learning and computational learning theory, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) a possible category as well.
